author: chamikara
msg: Users can register an object of this to get notified for special events (for e.g. RM faults, sequence time outs).

Corrected the timing out logic. Now a sequence can timeout when the maximum number of retransmissions exceed or depending on the last activated time. In a timeout, a registered SandeshaListner object will be invoked.

author: nadiramra
msg: C support fixes/enhancements. This commit makes method names consistent across all header files,
so that for a method METHOD in class CLASS, the generated C equivalent will be "axiscCLASSMETHOD".
